{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"98432d7c5b","title":"谈资本主义和社会主义经济","origin":"中国人民大学经济系政治经济学教研室编《中国资產阶级右派经济言论批判参考资料》，1958年9月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a79e6a3a99","index":0,"year":1957,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"98432d7c5b"}],"tags":[{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"35867de46f","name":"雷天觉"},{"id":"d01cee8eaf","name":"第一机械工业部"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"9faa584598","type":"title","text":"谈资本主义和社会主义经济","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98432d7c5b"},{"id":"b24a928a0b","type":"authors","text":"第一机械工业部雷天觉","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98432d7c5b"},{"id":"1961a4e919","type":"appellation","text":"（雷天觉：第一机械工业部机械科学研究院副院长，特级工程师）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98432d7c5b"},{"id":"ad8e432e17","type":"paragraph","text":"资本主义经济，供销有价值法则自动调节，社会主义经济是手动调节，自动比手动好，手动一有毛病就坏。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98432d7c5b"},{"id":"fbf23383c0","type":"paragraph","text":"社会主义生活好比洗淋浴，不是太热就是太冷，非常缺乏自动调节。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98432d7c5b"},{"id":"1f033c2cb5","type":"paragraph","text":"华尔街的势力这样大，是因为有一个证券交易所，交易所的活动起了一个客观价值的作用，价钱自定，用客观的方法决定价值。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98432d7c5b"},{"id":"80c57cc22c","type":"appellation","text":"（摘自马纪孔、薛政修、郭子诚〈驳斥资产阶级右派对计划经济的污蔑〉，载《计划经济》1957年第10期）","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98432d7c5b"}],"page":{"id":"bd9b17df18","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98432d7c5b","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}